{
  "page_title": "上下游关联客户信息-已添加客户",
  "apis": [
    {
      "group_title": "通过unionid和openid查询external_userid",
      "api_name": "unionid_to_external_userid",
      "method": "POST",
      "api_url": "https://qyapi.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/corpgroup/unionid_to_external_userid",
      "description": "通过unionid和openid查询external_userid",
      "query_params": [
        {
          "name": "access_token",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "上游应用的access_token"
        }
      ],
      "body_params": [
        {
          "name": "unionid",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "微信客户的unionid"
        },
        {
          "name": "openid",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "微信客户的openid"
        },
        {
          "name": "corpid",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "需要换取的企业corpid，不填则拉取所有企业"
        },
        {
          "name": "mass_call_ticket",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "[大批量调用凭据](#41709/获取接口高频调用凭据), 适用于数据初始化场景, 有获取及使用限制"
        }
      ],
      "response_params": [
        {
          "name": "errcode",
          "type": "int32",
          "required": false,
          "description": "返回码"
        },
        {
          "name": "errmsg",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "对返回码的文本描述内容"
        },
        {
          "name": "external_userid_info",
          "type": "object[]",
          "required": false,
          "description": "该unionid对应的外部联系人信息"
        },
        {
          "name": "external_userid_info.corpid",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "所属企业id"
        },
        {
          "name": "external_userid_info.external_userid",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "外部联系人id"
        }
      ],
      "request_examples": [
        {
          "title": "示例",
          "language": "json",
          "code": "{\n  \"unionid\":\"xxxxx\",\n  \"openid\":\"xxxxx\",\n  \"corpid\":\"xxxxx\",\n  \"mass_call_ticket\":\"xxxxx\"\n}"
        }
      ],
      "response_examples": [
        {
          "title": "示例",
          "language": "json",
          "code": "{\n \"errcode\":0,\n \"errmsg\":\"ok\",\n \"external_userid_info\":[\n \t\t{\n\t\t\t\"corpid\":\"AAAAA\",\n\t\t\t\"external_userid\":\"BBBB\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t{\n\t\t\t\"corpid\":\"CCCCC\",\n\t\t\t\"external_userid\":\"DDDDD\"\n\t\t}\n\t]\n}"
        }
      ],
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "external_userid的说明",
          "content": "external_userid是企业微信用于表示企业的外部联系人而设立的id，且满足以下条件\n假设同一个微信用户属于多个下游企业的外部联系人\n1.同一上游企业获取到不同企业的外部联系人的external_userid不一致。\n2.不同一上游企业获取同一个企业的同一个外部联系人的external_userid也不一致。"
        },
        {
          "title": "权限说明",
          "content": "调用该接口的应用必须是上下游共享的应用\n上游企业须已认证\nunionid（unionid的主体为绑定了该小程序的微信开放平台账号主体）和openid（即小程序账号主体）的主体需与当前企业的主体一致\nopenid与unionid必须是在同一个小程序获取到的\n应用需要具有客户联系权限\n自建应用/代开发应用可调用，第三方应用请查看企业客户微信unionid的升级方案\n调用频率最大为10万次/小时，48万次/天，750万次/月; 传入有效mass_call_ticket，可不受此限制, 但是依然受到基础频率限制。"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}